Adi Shankar -LRB- born Aditya Shankar ; January 8 , 1985 -RRB- is an Indian-born American film producer , film director , YouTube personality , and occasional actor , who is best known for being the youngest producer to have a number one film at the North American box office with The Grey .
He is also known for his `` Bootleg Universe '' fanfilms which includes The Punisher : Dirty Laundry , and Power/Rangers .
In 2014 Shankar ranked number 20 on GQ magazine 's list of `` Most Influential Global Indian Men . ''
He and Spencer Silna run the production company 1984 Private Defense Contractors .